h1. Description

This bundle provides the low level OSGi shell commands.

The following commands are available:
* bundles:headers - Display OSGi headers of a given bundle.
* bundles:info - Display detailed information of a given bundle.
* bundles:install - Install one or more bundles.
* bundles:list - List all installed bundles.
* bundles:refresh - Refresh bundles.
* bundles:resolve - Resolve bundles.
* bundles:restart - Stop and restart bundles.
* bundles:start - Starts bundles.
* bundle:start-level - Get or set the start level of a bundle.
* bundles:stop - Stop bundles.
* bundles:uninstall - Uninstall bundles.
* bundle:update - Update a bundle.

